short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Bring Call of Duty WWII to your browser! Download now for an immersive live wallpaper and a thrilling new tab experience.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Step into the battlefields of World War II! Download now for an action-packed Call of Duty WWII live wallpaper and enhance your new tab experience.

Relive the intensity of Call of Duty WWII with the WWII Live Wallpaper Chrome extension! Every new tab takes you straight to the frontlines, with dynamic and immersive wallpapers featuring iconic moments, soldiers, and battle scenes from the game. Feel the rush of combat with high-quality visuals that bring the historical intensity of WWII to your browser.

Key Features:
Dynamic WWII Live Wallpaper: Experience animated visuals from Call of Duty WWII, including intense combat scenes and soldiers in action.
Clock & Date Display: Stay organized while immersed in the action with an easy-to-read clock and date feature.
Quick Access Links: Access your favorite sites instantly with customizable, one-click shortcuts.
Convenient Features: Explore additional extensions, check the privacy policy, or uninstall the extension effortlessly.

Perfect for Call of Duty fans and history enthusiasts, this extension brings the epic battles of World War II to your new tab.

Download now and step into the historic fight with every new tab!
